KILLER BABY! - Who's Your Daddy? ►► http://bit.ly/1IIGemg

I've already played Five Nights at Freddy's, but you know who hasn't? Steph! I'm seeking vengeance for all the sabotages she has put me through by trolling her in her first ever play through of FNAF 2. Let's see how far she will get before she can't take it anymore. Revenge is a dish best served FNAF style.
